<div id="I_file">&lt;cstdlib&gt;</div>
<h1>EXIT_FAILURE</h1>
<div id="I_description">Failure termination code</div>
<section id="description">
This macro expands to a system-dependent integral expression that, when used as the argument for function <samp><a href="/exit">exit</a></samp>, signifies that the application failed.<br>
<br>
The opposite meaning can be specified with <samp><a href="/EXIT_SUCCESS">EXIT_SUCCESS</a></samp>.<br>
<div id="CH_bb"></div></div></div>
